property.name: text
property.value: Can you figure out how to double jump?

property.name: text
property.value: It's a checkpoint! Press X to swing your sword and activate it.

property.name: text
property.value: If you hit the spikes, you die!

property.name: text
property.value: See that black orb? If you break it in midair, you get your double jump back.

property.name: text
property.value: You can swing your sword in the air by holding a direction (up, down, left, right) and X. So cool!

property.name: text
property.value: If it isn't obvious from the spike pattern, you can walljump. Also, walljumping restores your double jump!

property.name: text
property.value: Oh, I just remembered something! You can press R to restart from the last checkpoint, but I'm sure you won't need it.

property.name: text
property.value: Oh, you can also hold up to climb walls. Sorry for not telling you earlier, but that might have been too helpful.

property.name: text
property.value: Psst...the secret tunnel is over here.
